OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FSam Blackledge reports on planned
OL,8,Fvoluntary redundancies at Devon's
OL,9,Fhospital trust
OL,11,FThe health trust which runs Devon's
OL,12,Flargest hospital is asking staff to
OL,13,Fconsider voluntary redundancy, saying
OL,14,Fit is facing a 'significant financial
OL,15,Fcrisis' which, if not addressed, could
OL,16,Fput patients at risk.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
