OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FLast week South Devon's MPs called on
OL,8,Fthe Health Secretary to act after the
OL,9,F'distressing' news that Torbay
OL,10,FHospital is offering staff redundancy
OL,11,Fpackages.
OL,13,FNow ITV West Country understands the
OL,14,FRoyal Devon University Trust is doing
OL,15,Fthe same, having revealed it is
OL,16,Ffailing to meet several performance
OL,17,Ftargets and overspending on staff
OL,18,Fcosts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FAn internal memo shows the trust is
OL,8,Fworried its workforce is growing at an
OL,9,F'unsustainable rate' and it is looking
OL,10,Fto reduce staff numbers by 400.
OL,12,FStaff have been told: "We must take
OL,13,Fdecisive and bold action now to break
OL,14,Fthe cycle to protect patient care.
OL,16,F"If we are not financially viable, we
OL,17,Fwill be unable to make the right
OL,18,Finvestments for the future, and the
OL,19,Fquality, safety and experience of care
OL,20,Fwe are able to offer to the 620,000
OL,21,Fpeople we serve will suffer."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe trust has launched a voluntary
OL,8,Fredundancy scheme, in the hope of
OL,9,Fshedding 400 jobs.
OL,11,FSteve Pulsford, head of operations at
OL,12,Fthe South West branch of the Royal
OL,13,FCollege of Nursing, said: "Staff in
OL,14,Fthe NHS have faced challenge after
OL,15,Fchallenge for more than a decade.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"This does have an increasing effect
OL,8,Fon them. They're seeing the impact on
OL,9,Fpatients in their communities, which
OL,10,Fthey serve. It's got a really, really
OL,11,Fsignificant impact on their morale at
OL,12,Fwork as well."
OL,14,FThe trust is now officially in
OL,15,F'turnaround' mode, meaning everything
OL,16,Fwill be reviewed to get the budget
OL,17,Fback on course.
OL,19,FThat means saving five per cent of the
OL,20,Fbudget every year for the next three
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FA spokesman for the trust said: "Like
OL,8,Fmany other trusts across Devon, the
OL,9,FRoyal Devon University Healthcare NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust has launched a
OL,11,Fvoluntary redundancy scheme.
OL,13,F"The trust is facing significant
OL,14,Ffinancial challenges and is
OL,15,Fimplementing a robust three-year
OL,16,Frecovery plan to restore financial
OL,17,Fstability, transform services and
OL,18,Fmodernise care to make sure that we
OL,19,Fcan deliver sustainable clinical
OL,20,Fservices for our patients.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"The trust is seeking to voluntarily
OL,8,Freduce staff numbers by 400. While the
OL,9,Fscheme is open to all colleagues, all
OL,10,Fapplications will be assessed to
OL,11,Fensure there is no impact on patient
OL,12,Fsafety or operational delivery as we
OL,13,Fremain focused on ensuring patient
OL,14,Fsafety and continuing to deliver
OL,15,Fcompassionate, high-quality care for
OL,16,Fall."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FA spokesman for Healthwatch Devon
OL,8,Fsaid: "From what we've been told, the
OL,9,Fvoluntary redundancy scheme is one of
OL,10,Fa number of steps being taken across
OL,11,FDevon to respond to ongoing financial
OL,12,Fpressures.
OL,14,F"It's time-limited and entirely
OL,15,Fvoluntary, with applications assessed
OL,16,Fto make sure patient safety and
OL,17,Fservices aren't affected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777359931
OL,3,CDevon hospital asks staff to consider
OL,4,Cvoluntary redundancy under recovery
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"More broadly, we recognise the system
OL,8,Fhas been working to manage a
OL,9,Fsignificant financial challenge over
OL,10,Frecent years, with a focus on
OL,11,Fefficiencies, new ways of working and
OL,12,Fservice improvements.
OL,14,F"At this stage, we haven't seen any
OL,15,Fclear or widespread impact on patient
OL,16,Fexperience linked to these
OL,17,Fdevelopments, but we'll keep this
OL,18,Funder close review."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
